Function reference

Main user functions

Main commands to communicate with JAMES.

james_post()
Make JAMES POST request
james_get()
Make JAMES GET request
inspect_demodata()
Inspect demo data uploaded to JAMES
read_json_js() read_json_jo()
Read JSON content from file or URL
valid_url()
Check for URL existence

Superseeded functions

Functions whose functionality has now been taken over.

download_as_list()
Download results from ocpu server as a list
get_url() get_url_svg()
Get url from OpenCPU response
request_chart()
Request a growth chart from JAMES
upload_txt()
Upload and parse data for JAMES
